MY MISSION STATEMENT


To provide exceptional investment guidance and service built on a foundation of trust, integrity, and professionalism.





My Story and Services


Michael W Butt
Help in achieving your financial vision...
Today's investment environment is increasingly complex. Because new opportunities abound experienced investment guidance is more important than ever. If you are like most investors, you need an advisor who has the knowledge and the skills to help you sort through and take advantage of investment opportunities that are right for you. As your financial advisor, I can provide advice and services that can help you achieve your financial goals. I take the time to understand your concerns, to advise you on the investment process and to create a strategy customized to your specific needs. Just as important, I know the value of keeping a long-term perspective on performance and following an investment strategy that is designed to weather varied market conditions. Fostering long-term client relationships based on trust and integrity is the benchmark of my business philosophy. I believe personal service is a chief contributor to achieving your goals.

BM/Supervisor; Securities Agent: AL, AR, AZ, CA, CO, CT, DC, DE, FL, GA, HI, IA, ID, IL, IN, KS, LA, MA, MD, ME, MI, MN, MS, MT, NC, NH, NJ, NM, NV, NY, OH, OK, OR, PA, SD, TN, TX, UT, VA, WA, WI, WY; General Securities Representative; Investment Advisor Representative; Transactional Futures/Commodities; Managed Futures
