Working With You


Working With You

CLIENT RELATIONSHIPS I view my relationship with you as a long-term commitment.  The initial interview and portfolio design, while important, are a small part of the much bigger picture. The real value I bring to clients is my insight and advice touching on all aspects of your financial affairs.PLANNING IS A PROCESS, NOT AN EVENTI believe that the most effective way to help you reach your unique financial vision is to consider all of your financial needs and objectives together.  As your advisor, I help you keep track of all aspects of your financial life.  Through meetings and frequent phone calls, we'll talk about your progress toward your financial goals.  And, when new situations require the modification of goals or strategies, I respond quickly and proactively to help ensure that your best interests are served.






